The paper deals with recommendation models, which are commonly studied in the sub-fields of machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The regularization technique is a common method used in machine learning and data science (cs.DS) to prevent overfitting and improve generalization. Finally, the paper focuses on improving the performance of recommender systems, which is a topic of interest in the sub-field of social and information networks (cs.SI).
